fm: int maxSubArrayLen(vector<int>& nums, int k)      {         unordered_map<long,vector<int>>Map;         long sum=0;         int result=INT_MIN;                  nums.insert(nums.begin(),0);                  for (int i=0; i<nums.size(); i++)         {             sum+=nums[i];             Map[sum].push_back(i);                          int temp = sum-k;             if (Map.find(temp)!=Map.end())             {                 result = max(result, i-Map[temp][0]);             }         }                  if (result==INT_MIN) result=0;                  return result;              }
